      "rationale": "Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) modeled with bilinear isotropic hardening; elastic modulus and yield stress calibrated from coupon tensile tests (n=6 per lot). Screw-rod interface represented with augmented Lagrange frictional contact (mu=0.2, validated separately). Model form assessed at level 3 consistent with nonlinear structural contact simulation of a Class II device."
