      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa ± 2.1 GPa) and yield stress (880 MPa ± 12 MPa) from lot-specific tensile coupons. Screw geometry verified by CMM to within 0.02 mm of nominal CAD. UHMWPE block geometry and fixture dimensions taken from certified ASTM F1717 fixture drawings. Uncertainty in material inputs propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000 samples); total input uncertainty contribution to stiffness QoI: ±3.4%."
