      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (Lab A: n=6, Lab B: n=5). All screws from the same production lot; dimensional inspection via CMM confirmed all critical dimensions within drawing tolerances. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness: 4.2%, indicating acceptable reproducibility."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
