      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA model inputs (geometry, material, BCs) demonstrably equivalent to experimental specimen and test configuration within stated uncertainty bounds.",
      "rationale": "CMM measurements of tested specimens compared against FEA geometry inputs; maximum dimensional discrepancy 0.03 mm on screw outer diameter. Material properties assigned from same production lot as tested specimens. Fixture geometry in FEA matches certified ASTM F1717 fixture drawings. Equivalency confirmed at level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
