      "rationale": "Three primary QoIs compared: stiffness (E/uval=1.41, 6.2% diff), yield force (E/uval=1.78, 8.7% diff), and force at 40 mm (E/uval=1.12, 5.1% diff). All three satisfy both acceptance criteria. Validation uncertainty (uval) computed following ASME V&V 20 methodology incorporating experimental measurement uncertainty, model parameter uncertainty, and numerical uncertainty. The methodology applied is consistent with the framework described in the peer-reviewed validation literature, including the comprehensive uncertainty quantification approach detailed in the methods reference cited in this assessment (see referencesIdentifier). Output comparison assessed at level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
